{"comments":"SIGIL wire format types for Hydrogen Scraper\n\nPort of Slide.Wire.Types to PureScript.\n\nEncoding scheme (from SIGIL spec):\n  0xxxxxxx  = hot token (ID in lower 7 bits, 0x00-0x7E)\n  10xxxxxx  = extended token (varint follows)\n  1100xxxx  = stream control\n  1101xxxx  = reserved\n  1110xxxx  = extension  \n  1111xxxx  = envelope (connection setup, rare)\n\nFor scraper data, we use a domain-specific extension:\n  0xE0 = COLOR (OKLCH: L/C/H/A as f16)\n  0xE1 = DIMENSION (Pixel as f32)\n  0xE2 = TRANSFORM (6 or 16 floats)\n  0xE3 = SHADOW (inset/offsets/blur/spread/color)\n  0xE4 = TRANSITION (from/to state + timing)\n  0xE5 = BOUNDING_BOX (x/y/w/h as f32)\n  0xE6 = ELEMENT_START (tag + selector)\n  0xE7 = ELEMENT_END\n  0xE8 = STATE_DIFF (changed properties)\n  0xE9 = ANIMATION (type + keyframes)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Token ID (for tokenized content, not used much in scraper)\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[68,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Scraper/Wire/Types.purs","start":[68,1]},"title":"TokenId"},{"children":[],"comments":"Hot token index (0-126)\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[71,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Scraper/Wire/Types.purs","start":[71,1]},"title":"HotId"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[75,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Scraper/Wire/Types.purs","start":[75,15]},"title":"Frame"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","d